      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Absolute Power",
        "Client": "Arctic Rescue Team",
        "Description": "We received an S.O.S. from\r\nseveral research team members\r\nstuck up in the mountains. A\r\nTigrex is on the prowl, keeping\r\nthem from coming down. There\u0027s\r\nno way we can rescue them until\r\nthat thing\u0027s been dealt with!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Tigrex",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Pouvoir absolu",
        "Client": "Secouristes en arctique",
        "Description": "On a re\u00E7u un S.O.S. d\u0027une\r\n\u00E9quipe de recherche coinc\u00E9e dans\r\nles montagnes. Un Tigrex les\r\nbloque, ils ne peuvent pas\r\nredescendre. On a besoin de toi.\r\n\u00C9limine le Tigrex, s\u0027il te pla\u00EEt !",
